{"title": "Serious games for training, rehabilitation and workforce development.", "fields": ["3d user interaction", "workforce development", "virtual reality", "leverage", "patient safety"], "abstract": "We present a set of demonstrations of current work in the Clemson University Virtual Environments Group involving the development and testing of interactive virtual environments for applications in training, rehabilitation and workforce development. All of these applications are designed to leverage commodity hardware such as HDTVs, game controllers, and the Kinect sensor.", "citation": "Citations (1)", "departments": ["Clemson University", "Clemson University", "Clemson University", "Clemson University", "Clemson University"], "authors": ["Jeffrey W. Bertrand.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/b/Bertrand:Jeffrey_W=", "Lauren Cairco Dukes.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/d/Dukes:Lauren_Cairco", "Patrick S. Dukes.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/d/Dukes:Patrick_S=", "Elham Ebrahimi.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/e/Ebrahimi:Elham", "Austen L. Hayes.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/h/Hayes:Austen_L=", "Naja Mack.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/m/Mack:Naja", "Jerome McClendon.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/m/McClendon:Jerome", "Dhaval Parmar.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/p/Parmar:Dhaval", "Toni Bloodworth Pence.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/p/Pence:Toni_Bloodworth", "Blair Shannon.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/s/Shannon:Blair", "Aliceann Wachter.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/w/Wachter:Aliceann", "Yanxiang Wu.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/w/Wu:Yanxiang", "Sabarish V. Babu.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/b/Babu:Sabarish_V=", "Larry F. Hodges.....http://dblp.org/pers/hd/h/Hodges:Larry_F="], "conf": "vr", "year": "2013", "pages": 2}